{"tid":2122898,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［轉載］太空人計劃詳情","createTime":"2020-07-24T09:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T16:39:21.000Z","uid":117420,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b74dd68edf68eacaf91a562eef05576b4fd0cd8d","tid":2122898,"uid":117420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T09:16:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/108411397560878/posts/151242569944427/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F108411397560878%2Fposts%2F151242569944427%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6H4fze6eI6Am6%2FUgKT%2BdzFE%3D&h=c5853f84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/108411397560878/posts/151242569944427/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n太空人會影響小朋友申請求居！<br />\n太空人會影響小朋友申請求居！<br />\n太空人會影響小朋友申請求居！<br />\n<br />\n就太空人的問題，網上眾說紛紜。翻看條例後，此舉會影響18歲以下子女將來申請永居。<br />\n<br />\n特意查看了現時兒童申請永居的要求，根據(Immigration rules part 8, clause 298)：<br />\n<br />\n兒童（18歲以下）申請永居條件： <br />\n<br />\n(a) both parents are present and settled in the United Kingdom; or (父母雙方皆已有永居,最正常情況）<br />\n<br />\n跳至C項 （類似太空人情況）<br />\n(c) one parent is present and settled in the United Kingdom and has had sole responsibility for the child&rsquo;s upbringing or the child normally lives with this parent and not their other parent; or<br />\n<br />\n好啦，很多人話，我一個人在英國做太空人照顧小朋友,同佢一齊住，咪符合C囉。<br />\n<br />\n錯，內政部對咩係sole responsibility and child normally lives with this parent 係有定義的。<br />\n<br />\n即是要： <br />\n- sole responsibility 指父母其中一方負責兒童的重要決定，通常指放棄撫養權<br />\n- child normally lives with this parent and not their other parent 通常指已離異的父母，但有共同撫養權<br />\n<br />\n咁如果真係咁，5年後小朋友不能永居點算？唔通要離開英國？我都唔太清楚，估計是申請成為已拿永居的父/母的dependent?<br />\n<br />\n咁如果父母都有BNO，子女為dependent，必須一同申請嗎？<br />\n唔知，有人說跟family visa類比就要，如果與PBS dependent （如工作簽證dependent)即可分開申請。<br />\n<br />\n以上只供參考，請留意一月細節公佈。如果情況比較複雜者，建議向有牌adviser 查詢。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/find-an-immigration-adviser\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Ffind-an-immigration-adviser&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6H4fze6eI6Am6%2FUgKT%2BdzFE%3D&h=b75cef32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/find-an-immigration-adviser</a><br />\n<br />\n詳細定義請見 (p. 36 - 38): <a href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/902835/family-life-_as-a-partner-or-parent_-private-life-and-exceptional-circs-v9.0ext.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.publishing.service.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fuploads%2Fsystem%2Fuploads%2Fattachment_data%2Ffile%2F902835%2Ffamily-life-_as-a-partner-or-parent_-private-life-and-exceptional-circs-v9.0ext.pdf&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6H4fze6eI6Am6%2FUgKT%2BdzFE%3D&h=a0b4e60e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/902835/family-life-_as-a-partner-or-parent_-private-life-and-exceptional-circs-v9.0ext.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"d571465bc70712669952abd22087586fa6aafdab","tid":2122898,"uid":117420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T09:16:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8bf2fe4528255974ad42be612dce3191dc262958","tid":2122898,"uid":117420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T09:16:22.000Z","msg":"繼續推"},{"pid":"a7618d404ee406b9f904ede5d269f918433e413d","tid":2122898,"uid":117420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T09:16:34.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"f8cf83276019db2e8de18f7c30dc08aaaf38c607","tid":2122898,"uid":301989,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T09:17:31.000Z","msg":"乜嘢係太空人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec0ff6fcaeb0500703674a7200eb1512309e649","tid":2122898,"uid":117420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f8cf83276019db2e8de18f7c30dc08aaaf38c607","tid":2122898,"uid":301989,"like":3,"d